      <li>Game  <span class="math">G_2</span> : This game behaves as in  <span class="math">G_1</span>  except for another change in the accept condition. We accept if f(x') = 1 and ZK proofs of step 13 verifies and Z is the one-key of the output wire, and the commitment in step 8 is correctly opened to Z (i.e. no  <span class="math">K_i&#x27; = K_i^{x_i}</span>  check).    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-300 my-2 ml-4">
