      <li>The two games are indistinguishable due to the second condition in the <em>correctness</em> property of the garbling scheme. Note that we are also implicitly using the committing OT property (the protocol described in the COT hybrid model) as the keys extracted in the OTs and what the functionality sends to the honest prover are the same.</li>
